transcript.text: Welcome to Onprint Shop.
We will see under store personalization promotional content message.
We will see what is promotional content message, How to add promotional content message, How to manage promotional content message, What is a promotional content message?
So a promotional content message is a marketing strategy developed by a business to promote a product or service.
So let's see how you can use promotional message or content to promote your product or service on your website.
So by the help of a promotional message like this one over here for the seasonal option, you can promote your product or service on your website.
Let's say over here the coupon code is generated and added in the promotional message to avail the 50% flat discount.

So to promote a product or a coupon or a discount you have created, you can use promotional message content to promote them and you can promote them with the help of a pop up like this or a slider like this.
You can see a slider over here that is for free shipping for minimum purchase of $500.
Or you can create a toggle like this.
You can see a togle on right hand side.
So you can create a toggle like this or a header promotional message like this.
So now you can create a promotional message, but from where and how?
So for that you will need to go to Admin panel.
First of all you will need to go to Store Configuration Settings.
From settings you need to search for promotional.
So you will get over here to enable the promotional message section, select Yes.
From here click on Save then go to Store Personalization promotional content message.
From here you can add a promotional content message.
To add a promotional content message click on add button in top right hand corner.
From here you will need to select available to.
So it will be available to both retailer and corporates or only retailer or only corporates.
Then when it should be displayed?

Before login, after login or both before and after login then you will need to select on which page this promotional message should be displayed so that you can select from here like say content pages, static page, category, group product page, Suppose product page then you select product page then the product from here.
Or you can also select like say all products or all content pages or all pages.
After selecting this you'll need to select the promotional pattern.
So will it be a pop up like this one or a slider like this one or a toggle like this one or a top header message.
So you select from here.
Suppose you select a slider, then you will need to select the position of the slider like top left, top right, bottom left, bottom right.
I'll select pop up over here.
So I'll need to add the height and width of the pop up in pixels.
Or I can directly put it to auto.
So when I add auto it will auto generate the size of the pop up.
Now comes the time.

So time is the time till which the promotional message will not be displayed once promotional message is closed by the user and if no input is there and then promotion will be displayed every time after this time interval.
So I'll select one minute here then the delay time.
So delay time is the time after which a pop up will appear when a customer lands on a page.
So I'll set delay time one second then title.
So I'll add a title over here 38 and I was sorry and in the description I can add the description in words like availa discount or I can add a image.
So I'll direct add a image over here by clicking on the image button from here.
Then go to upload design, choose the file, send it to the server and click on OK so the image is added.
Now I want to add a link of a product page on this image.
So I'll go to the product page, select the link and add the link by clicking on this link button at the link over here and then click on OK.
So link is added to the popup.
Now when the customer will click on the popup, he will be redirected to the product page and status IQ.
So here the product I have selected is business card.
Now save and back.
So you can see over here the popup is added.
Now when I go to the storefront, you can see the pop up is available over here for the customer.
And when customer clicks on this pop up, he'll be redirected to the product page of the business card.
So this is how you can add a promotional content message.

And if you want to edit a promotional content message, just go to promotional content message over here, click on Action button, click on edit button and you can edit or manage promotional message from here.
Thank you for watching this video.
